1.12
log
@Allow for abbreviated FIBs
@
text
@/* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * */
/* |_o_o|\\ Copyright (c) 1987, 1988 The Software Distillery.  All Rights  */
/* |. o.| || Reserved.  This program may not be distributed without the    */
/* | .  | || permission of the authors:                            BBS:    */
